{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 294072, "create_time": 1657791035, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "通过换票，乘务员就会知道，这个卧铺有没有人，及时统计未使用的床铺，并将其调整到需要床铺的人手里，如老弱病残孕等特殊人群。", "timestamp": 1657791035}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 294076, "create_time": 1657791113, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "提醒睡着的人别坐过站", "timestamp": 1657791113}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 294079, "create_time": 1657791143, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "还有现在卧铺也要换票吧", "timestamp": 1657791143}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 294080, "create_time": 1657791216, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "我有幸换过一次哈哈", "timestamp": 1657791216}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 294111, "create_time": 1657792883, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "AB正解，查验车票核实乘客，统计空铺便于继续出售车票，代为保管并提醒旅客到站下车。现在由于广泛采用了电子客票，这些信息可以更为方便地统计，所以大部分列车卧铺已经不再换票了，bot回来那趟车就没有换票。至于以前有电子售票系统却还要换票，我认为主要是因为在验票进站时，大多闸机只支持纸质车票，所以无法统计真实上车情况，所以现在设备升级之后就不需要了。", "timestamp": 1657792883}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 294120, "create_time": 1657793185, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "为了让你弄丢了卡片赔工本费50元🐶🐶🐶", "timestamp": 1657793185}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 294137, "create_time": 1657793927, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "虽然2010版《铁路旅客运输规程》中仍规定需要换票，但是在《铁路旅客电子客票暂行实施办法》中已经明确“对于乘坐卧铺的旅客，列车工作人员应通过手持终端为旅客办理卧铺使用登记和到站提醒业务。”基本告别需要换票的时代。", "timestamp": 1657793927}], "create_time": 1657789067, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1657793927, "likenum": 5, "n_attentions": 5, "n_comments": 7, "pid": 83040, "poll": null, "reply": 7, "text": "#博物bot\n#假期篇-十万个为什么\n这个问题来源于bot坐火车回家时的疑问：为什么以前的火车卧铺需要换票？", "timestamp": 1657789067}}